Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveA Total filling station around Delabo Junction, Ilisan-Remo in the Ikenne Local Government Area of Ogun came under attack, and two guards were killed Sunday night.
The following day, residents woke up to discover the corpses of the victims—and the assailants took nothing from the station, according to neighbours.
Police have not been briefed.
The state Police Public Relations Officer  Abimbola Oyeyemi he was yet to receive the situation report.
